		p Yue Guan is a PhD candidate at Tsinghua University, China, and he is working at Joint Institute For Regional Earth System Science and Engineering, UCLA as a visiting student. Yue received his B.S. Degree in Tsinghua University. His major is numerical simulation on dispersion of radioactive pollutant in ocean.
