		p Gautham Badhrinathan is doing his Masters in Computer Science at University of California, Los Angeles. He received his B.E. degree in Electronics and Communications Engineering from Birla Institute of Technology and Science, Dubai Campus (BITS Pilani, Dubai Campus).
		p Gautham worked as a Software Developer Intern at Environmental Systems Research Institute (Esri) for six months. Over there he developed web applications that dealt with Georeferencing and Classifying Satelite Imagery. He also worked on extending their core desktop product.
